One and a half years ago she was kidnapped by the Russian Secret Services from the territory of Ukraine and illegally brought to Russia. The Russian authorities incriminate to her the crimes she had never committed. There are no independent courts in Russia, and the judges follow the commands from Kremlin. It is the third time that Nadiya declares a hunger strike, this time ¬Ñ dry hunger strike. In the best of cases she will be able to live for another 7-8 days.
